  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722030/extras/380f88add7c0a90cee32be80253ac8a1.avif?t=1745015342\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722030/extras_big/380f88add7c0a90cee32be80253ac8a1.avif?t=1745015342 width=800 height=1992 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide hapless knights to a hungry treasure chest mimic by placing directional tiles, springs, and boxes to avoid obstacles and enemies getting in the way of the knights and their treasure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 challenging levels with fun cut scenes, 4 different knights with different personalities, a great soundtrack, and all the puns you can tolerate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A collaboration between Rigg'd Games and Lowtek Games.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722030/extras/380f88add7c0a90cee32be80253ac8a1.avif?t=1745015342\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722030/extras_big/380f88add7c0a90cee32be80253ac8a1.avif?t=1745015342 width=800 height=1992 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide hapless knights to a hungry treasure chest mimic by placing directional tiles, springs, and boxes to avoid obstacles and enemies getting in the way of the knights and their treasure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 challenging levels with fun cut scenes, 4 different knights with different personalities, a great soundtrack, and all the puns you can tolerate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A collaboration between Rigg'd Games and Lowtek Games.</p>",
